327
00:25:09,243 --> 00:25:11,712
不。不。
No. No.

328
00:25:13,914 --> 00:25:14,914
来吧。
Come on.

329
00:25:26,394 --> 00:25:28,062
他把我的系统锁在外面了。
He locked me out of my system.

330
00:25:31,032 --> 00:25:32,400
好工作,奥兰多。
Good work, Orlando.

331
00:25:32,433 --> 00:25:37,304
有些人称之为魔法，我称之为擅长工作。
Some people call it magic, I call it being good at my job.

332
00:25:44,612 --> 00:25:47,248
红色警报，全体准备!
Code red, all hands on deck!

333
00:25:49,650 --> 00:25:51,886
很好，你们俩。
Very good, you two.

334
00:25:53,621 --> 00:25:57,291
人类屁股顶着火焰能做出的事真是太神奇了。
It's amazing what humans can do with their asses up against the flame.

335
00:25:57,324 --> 00:25:59,894
