Tell me what the hell is going on.

336
00:25:59,927 --> 00:26:02,596
你喜欢电影吗，奥兰多?
You like movies, Orlando?

337
00:26:02,630 --> 00:26:04,432
我现在才不管什么电影。
I don't give a shit about movies right now.

338
00:26:04,465 --> 00:26:06,834
我真的很喜欢《现代启示录》。
I really like Apocalypse Now.

339
00:26:09,937 --> 00:26:15,409
我有点像威拉德，顺流而下完成我的任务。
You know, I'm kinda like Willard, floating down the river to complete my mission.

340
00:26:15,443 --> 00:26:19,847
而你，嗯，我…我猜你和我被困在船上了。
And you, well, I... I guess you're stuck on the boat with me.

341
00:26:21,248 --> 00:26:22,917
