What is this?

342
00:26:22,950 --> 00:26:25,853
必须以极端的偏见消除外来者。
Outsiders must be eliminated with extreme prejudice.

343
00:26:27,922 --> 00:26:30,858
-我只是来看恩佐的。-不，不，不，别走
- I just came to see Enzo. - No, no, no, don't go.

344
00:26:30,891 --> 00:26:36,230
那我想你最好表现得特别好，好让我改变主意，不杀你。
Oh, then I guess you better be extra good, so I change my mind and don't kill you.

345
00:26:39,600 --> 00:26:41,503
这是一个好女孩。
That's a good girl.

346
00:26:41,536 --> 00:26:44,638
现在去找个地方坐下来欣赏表演吧。
Now go take a seat and enjoy the show.

347
00:26:45,840 --> 00:26:48,175
——这是正确的。-会没事的
- That's right. - It's gonna be okay.

348
00:26:54,583 --> 00:26:58,285
好了，奥兰多，屏幕上的数字。
Now, Orlando, the numbers on your screen.

349
00:26:59,420 --> 00:27:03,624
我要你从你刚黑进那个账户的钱里转两百万。
I want you to transfer $2 million from the funds you just hacked into that account.

350
00:27:04,758 --> 00:27:06,193
这需要时间。
It's gonna take time.

351
00:27:06,227 --> 00:27:08,762
别瞎扯了。你有五分钟时间。
Don't bullshit a bullshitter. You have five minutes.

352
00:27:10,464 --> 00:27:16,337
清楚……当我叫你叫的时候，你唯一的问题应该是，“叫多大声?”
Be clear... When I tell you to bark, your only question should be, "How loud?"

353
00:27:17,771 --> 00:27:19,373
我要准备下一个任务了。
I'm gonna prep our next mission.

354
00:27:19,406 --> 00:27:20,708
河下游见。
See you down the river.

355
00:27:34,556 --> 00:27:36,257
嘿。
Hey.

356
00:27:36,290 --> 00:27:37,391
嘿,艾娃。
Hey, Ava.

357
00:27:39,193 --> 00:27:43,130
有同事发现你不见了吗?
Hey, is there anyone at work that might notice you're missing?

358
00:27:45,366 --> 00:27:47,602
——没有人?——没有。
- No one? - No.

359
00:27:47,636 --> 00:27:49,803
我的老板今天不在。
My-my boss isn't in today.

360
00:27:50,671 --> 00:27:55,743
唯一知道我在这里的人是…不，不，先生，不，不。
The only person that knows I'm here is... No, no, sir, sir. No, no.

361
00:27:55,776 --> 00:27:58,245
我明明说的是熏牛肉，不是腊肠。
I-I clearly said pastrami, not salami.

362
00:27:58,279 --> 00:28:00,549
-我是说，我理解…恩佐,恩佐。
- I-I mean, I understand... - Enzo, Enzo.

363
00:28:00,582 --> 00:28:02,349
那不是我的……耶稣!
That's not my... Jesus!

364
00:28:02,383 --> 00:28:03,684
他妈的什么?
What the fuck?

365
00:28:06,621 --> 00:28:12,726
好吧，艾娃，我很抱歉，但你不能这样出现在我的工作现场。
Okay, uh, Ava, I'm really sorry, but you cannot show up to my work like this.

366
00:28:12,760 --> 00:28:16,263
——这是…-他的座位下面有个炸弹。
- This is... - There's a bomb under his seat.

367
00:28:16,297 --> 00:28:17,331
什么?
What?

368
00:28:19,166 --> 00:28:22,604
-她在说什么?-新闻里的公园炸弹客。
- What's she talking about? - Park bomber on the news.

369
00:28:22,637 --> 00:28:23,971
我想这就是他。
I think this is him.

370
00:28:29,476 --> 00:28:30,778
哦,狗屎。
Oh, shit.

371
00:28:33,548 --> 00:28:35,049
我要吐了。
I'm gonna be sick.

372
00:28:35,082 --> 00:28:37,552
奥兰多，别让他走。
Orlando, don't let him leave.

373
00:28:37,586 --> 00:28:41,055
-搞什么鬼?!-嘿，恩佐，如果你走，我们都得死。
- What the fuck?! - Hey, Enzo, if you leave, we're all dead.

374
00:28:41,088 --> 00:28:43,958
——耶稣,伙计!-恩佐，听我说。
- Jesus, dude! - Enzo, please, listen.

375
00:28:43,991 --> 00:28:45,993
听?你他妈听到墙里的声音了吗?
Listen? Listen to the fucking voice in the walls?

376
00:28:46,026 --> 00:28:47,672
你他妈今天在这里干什么?
What the fuck are you even doing here today?

377
00:28:47,696 --> 00:28:49,096
你的办公室关门了!
Your-your office is closed!

378
00:28:50,064 --> 00:28:54,134
等等，哇，哇，哇……你是…贱人，你也参与了吗?
Wait-wait, whoa, whoa, whoa... Are you... Bitch, are you part of this?

379
00:28:54,168 --> 00:28:56,003
-我什么?!-你为什么在这里?
- Am I what?! - Why are you here?!

380
00:28:56,036 --> 00:28:58,806
我在找你，你这个混蛋!
Looking for you, you asshole!

381
00:28:58,839 --> 00:29:00,675
嘿,嘿,嘿。
Hey, hey, hey.

382
00:29:00,709 --> 00:29:02,219
我才是有能力帮你的人。
I'm the one who's got the skills to help you.

383
00:29:02,243 --> 00:29:05,145
不是他们。让他们去。
Not them. Let 'em go.

384
00:29:05,179 --> 00:29:07,281
恩佐，别进去。
Hey, Enzo, don't go in there.

385
00:29:07,314 --> 00:29:09,450
对不起,兄弟。我很抱歉。我不能……我做不到。
I'm sorry, bro. I'm sorry. I can't... I can't do it.

386
00:29:09,483 --> 00:29:10,727
我帮你叫警察。好吧?
I'll call the cops for you. Okay?

387
00:29:10,751 --> 00:29:12,319
如果你进去，我们都会死。
If you go in there, we're all dead.

388
00:29:12,353 --> 00:29:14,388
是聪明的。恩佐,不!
Be smart. Enzo, no!

389
00:29:15,356 --> 00:29:16,591
我很抱歉。对不起。
I'm sorry. Sorry.

390
00:29:17,659 --> 00:29:18,627
好吧。
Okay.

391
00:29:18,660 --> 00:29:20,261
艾娃,失望!
Ava, down!

392
00:29:21,295 --> 00:29:22,429
恩佐,不!
Enzo, no!

393
00:29:43,984 --> 00:29:45,986
我就知道!这是军事。
I knew it! It's military.

394
00:29:46,020 --> 00:29:48,255
只是不是现代军队。
Just not modern military.

395
00:29:48,289 --> 00:29:49,790
越南的时代。
Vietnam era.

396
00:29:49,823 --> 00:29:51,726
压力敏感。
Pressure sensitive.

397
00:29:51,760 --> 00:29:53,193
越共曾经使用过。
Viet Cong used to use them.

398
00:29:53,227 --> 00:29:57,197
在扳机上放一根羽毛，试着把它取下来，嘭。
Put so much as a feather weight on the trigger, try and take it off, kaboom.

399
00:29:57,231 --> 00:30:00,034
该死的!就像圣经里说的那样。
Damn! That's like Biblical old.

400
00:30:00,067 --> 00:30:02,604
就像我参加玛士撒拉的成人礼一样。
That's like I was at Methuselah's bar mitzvah old.

401
00:30:02,637 --> 00:30:05,139
这是四个音节，玛士撒拉，哦。
Those are four syllables, Methuselah, ooh.

402
00:30:05,172 --> 00:30:07,217
是啊，我帮他泡妞了。我是第一个帮他泡妞的人。
Yeah, I got him laid. I was the first guy to get him laid.

403
00:30:07,241 --> 00:30:08,510
我敢打赌。
I bet.

404
00:30:08,543 --> 00:30:10,712
-我哥哥从越南回来了。——是吗?
- My big brother came back from 'Nam. - Yeah?

405
00:30:10,745 --> 00:30:14,582
他教了我这些爆炸性的东西，把它变成了我们的爱好。
He kinda taught me all this explosive stuff, made it kind of a hobby for us.

406
00:30:14,616 --> 00:30:18,720
-这就解释了很多。-哦,是的。我们是纵火。
- That explains a lot. - Oh, yeah. We were pyromaniacs.

407
00:30:18,753 --> 00:30:21,756
你炸的够多了，你的电线也会交叉。
You blow enough shit up, your wires will be crossed, too.

408
00:30:21,790 --> 00:30:23,223
好吧。
Okay.

409
00:30:23,257 --> 00:30:28,362
嗯,那又怎样?我们去了每个退伍军人互助小组问他们谁的肩膀上有碎片，还是怎样?
Um, so what? We head to every veteran's support group and ask who's got a chip on their shoulder, or what?

410
00:30:28,395 --> 00:30:32,132
当然，我们可以一边做一边举办烘焙义卖。
Sure, we can host a bake sale while we're at it.

411
00:30:32,166 --> 00:30:35,936
事实上，我觉得你会喜欢搜身那些老兵的。
Actually, I think you might enjoy patting those vets down.

412
00:30:35,969 --> 00:30:37,338
做个体腔检查什么的。
Give a cavity search, whatever.

413
00:30:37,371 --> 00:30:39,073
哦，是的，我喜欢。
Oh, yeah, love it.

414
00:30:39,106 --> 00:30:41,475
不如等鉴证科的指纹出来再说?
Why don't we just wait for a fingerprint from forensics?

415
00:30:41,509 --> 00:30:44,278
所有单位，前往哈德逊塔。
All units, proceed to Hudson Tower.

416
00:30:45,946 --> 00:30:49,149
发生了爆炸。再重复一遍,所有单位。
There's been an explosion. Repeat, all units.

417
00:30:50,518 --> 00:30:53,320
我们有一块奶酪。一定会有披萨的。
We got a piece of cheese. There's gotta be a pizza.

418
00:31:05,800 --> 00:31:07,301
这是怎么呢
What's going on?

419
00:31:17,645 --> 00:31:20,648
这首歌献给你的老朋友。
This one goes out to that late buddy of yours.

420
00:31:20,682 --> 00:31:22,416
再见,恩佐。
Bye-bye, Enzo.

421
00:31:22,449 --> 00:31:24,819
恩佐!恩佐!
Enzo! Enzo!

422
00:31:33,026 --> 00:31:35,162
放松。
Easy, now.

423
00:31:36,463 --> 00:31:37,632
艾娃!
Ava!

424
00:31:37,665 --> 00:31:40,535
艾娃，能听到我说话吗?
Ava, can you hear me?

425
00:31:40,568 --> 00:31:42,537
你还好吗?
Are you okay?

426
00:31:42,570 --> 00:31:45,305
为什么?天花板的一部分砸到你的头，你会生气吗?
Why? Would you be after part of the ceiling hit you in the head?

427
00:31:45,339 --> 00:31:50,612
这是一个遗憾。但这也不是第一次有人因为你的罪过而堕落了。
It's a pity. But it wouldn't be the first time others have fallen for your sins.

428
00:31:50,645 --> 00:31:53,882
你杀了他，你个混蛋!他什么也没做!
You killed him, you son of a bitch! He didn't do anything!

429
00:31:53,914 --> 00:31:57,184
哦,请。你认识他吗?
Oh, please. Did you even know him?

430
00:31:57,217 --> 00:32:00,287
还是对你来说，他只是另一个无名的程序?
Or was he just another nameless, faceless program to you?

431
00:32:00,320 --> 00:32:06,460
你也许从没杀过人，奥兰多，但你夺走的生命比我想象的还要多。
You may have never murdered anyone, Orlando, but you have taken more lives than I could ever dream of.

432
00:32:08,195 --> 00:32:10,364
你会为此付出代价的，你个混蛋。
You're gonna pay for this, you son of a bitch.

433
00:32:10,397 --> 00:32:13,500
-你会为此付出代价的我是- - - ?
- You're gonna pay for this. - Am I?

434
00:32:13,535 --> 00:32:17,337
你屁股上绑了足够的C4炸药是第一个登上火星的人。
You're the one with enough C4 strapped to your ass to be the first man on Mars.

435
00:32:19,306 --> 00:32:23,076
对不起，我就是忍不住。
Sorry, I just couldn't resist.

436
00:32:27,381 --> 00:32:29,751
好了，来吧，别废话了。
All right, come on, let's cut the shit.

437
00:32:29,784 --> 00:32:33,855
911事件后，LCPD的反应时间是7分钟。
LCPD response time to something of our nature post-9/11 is seven minutes.

438
00:32:33,888 --> 00:32:36,591
加上圣诞节的流量，最多15辆。
With Christmas traffic, we've got 15 max.

439
00:32:36,624 --> 00:32:37,926
你怎么知道的?
How do you know?

440
00:32:37,958 --> 00:32:40,127
今早公园里的炸弹?
That bomb in the park this morning?

441
00:32:42,831 --> 00:32:47,334
你必须测试这些东西，否则它们可能会……砰!
You gotta test these things out, or they might go... Bang!

442
00:32:47,367 --> 00:32:50,270
你该庆幸是你的老朋友维克多而不是你。
Just be glad it was your old pal Victor and not you.

443
00:32:50,304 --> 00:32:54,374
——维克多?-或者我应该说v -浩劫?
- Victor? - Or should I say V-Havoc?

444
00:32:54,408 --> 00:32:57,579
你们俩以前可是黑帽帮的得力助手。
You two were quite the black hat team back in the day.

445
00:33:03,952 --> 00:33:07,020
你们俩都没有得到应得的惩罚，对吧?
Neither one of you got the sentence you deserved, did you?

446
00:33:10,257 --> 00:33:12,226
虽然他被赦免了罪。
Thought he was absolved from sin.

447
00:33:12,259 --> 00:33:14,461
回到日常生活。
Back to the daily routine.

448
00:33:14,495 --> 00:33:20,234
早上六点慢跑，六点四十五喝咖啡，七点十五在公园看新闻。
Six AM jog, 6:45 coffee, 7:15 news in the park.

449
00:33:21,803 --> 00:33:26,240
我想，我们是有习惯的生物，是福也是祸。
We are creatures of habit, a blessing and a curse, I suppose.

450
00:33:26,273 --> 00:33:29,343
这是什么，仇杀吗?
So what is this, a vendetta?

451
00:33:29,376 --> 00:33:31,746
在你看来，这是份工作。
As far as you're concerned, this is a job.

452
00:33:31,779 --> 00:33:36,350
我花了很长时间研究你的习惯。
A job I've spent a very long time studying your habits for.

453
00:33:36,383 --> 00:33:38,553
你真的应该多待在家里。
You really should spend more time at home.

454
00:33:39,888 --> 00:33:46,794
我猜你希望只要再给你一次机会就能挽救你的婚姻。
I'm guessing you wish you could fix that marriage of yours if you just had one more shot.

455
00:33:53,267 --> 00:33:55,603
二百万美元。
Two million dollars.

456
00:33:56,470 --> 00:34:00,274
你可以去某个小岛上养老。
You can go retire on an island somewhere.

457
00:34:00,307 --> 00:34:03,978
在现在的经济状况下，你不能靠两百万退休。
You can't retire on two million in this economy.

458
00:34:04,012 --> 00:34:08,315
再说了，那钱不是给我的，是给你的。
Besides, that money wasn't for me, that was for you.

459
00:34:10,350 --> 00:34:11,350
哦,狗屎。
Oh, shit.

460
00:34:12,921 --> 00:34:14,121
你做了什么?
What have you done?

461
00:34:14,154 --> 00:34:16,156
你赢得了它。
You earned it.

462
00:34:16,189 --> 00:34:19,661
警察会同意的，但我想要更多。
The police would agree, but I want more.

463
00:34:27,001 --> 00:34:29,637
圣堂武士债券?我不明白你的意思。
Templar Bonds? I don't understand.

464
00:34:29,671 --> 00:34:32,707
你刚刚可以进入一家银行。你为什么想要债券?
You-you just had access to a bank. Why would you want bonds?

465
00:34:32,740 --> 00:34:35,409
我才不管什么债券，你个白痴。
I don't give a shit about bonds, you idiot.

466
00:34:35,442 --> 00:34:38,846
我想拥有所有者。
I want to own the owners.

467
00:34:38,880 --> 00:34:42,115
我想让所有的小猪都生活在恐惧中。
I want all the little pigs to live in fear for a change.

468
00:34:42,149 --> 00:34:44,852
我要我的靴子踩在他们的脖子上。
I want my boots on their fucking neck.

469
00:34:44,886 --> 00:34:53,561
我要他们的钱，他们的信息，锁在他们的小保险箱里。
I want their money, I want their information, locked away in their little security deposit boxes.

470
00:34:53,595 --> 00:34:55,495
你想要他们的服务器。
You want their servers.

471
00:34:55,530 --> 00:34:59,867
唯一能找到那些在单独加密的硬盘上有访问密码的盒子。
And the only way to those with access codes on individually encrypted drives in those boxes.

472
00:35:01,636 --> 00:35:03,004
完全难以捉摸的。
Perfectly untraceable.

473
00:35:03,037 --> 00:35:12,212
所有人都在6点安全网络触手可及的范围内，你要在60分钟内锁定之前帮我渗透并驱散这个网络。
All within an arm's reach of a six-point security grid, a grid that you will infiltrate and diffuse for me before it locks in 60 minutes.

474
00:35:13,380 --> 00:35:16,618
-你疯了。-我是个乐观主义者。
- You're crazy. - I'm an optimist.

475
00:35:18,318 --> 00:35:20,220
我需要更多的准备。
I need more prep.

476
00:35:20,253 --> 00:35:25,392
-我需要更多装备。-你浪费的时间越多，特警就越快冲进来，用枪扫射。
- I need more gear. - The more time you waste, the sooner SWAT bursts in, guns blazing.

477
00:35:25,425 --> 00:35:27,327
你觉得他们会先问问题吗?
You think they'll ask questions first?

478
00:35:36,037 --> 00:35:37,137
好吗?
Well?

479
00:35:37,170 --> 00:35:40,074
好吧，我来做。
All right, I'll do it.

480
00:35:40,108 --> 00:35:41,776
好男孩。
Good boy.

481
00:35:48,883 --> 00:35:50,283
你他妈在干什么?
What the fuck are you doing?

