他们可不想在电视直播中爆了你的头。
They don't want to blow your brains out on live TV.

643
00:48:06,521 --> 00:48:11,726
看来我们的游戏进入了下一个阶段，因为现在他们终于认真对待我们了。
Well, it seems that we've reached the next phase of our game, because now they're finally taking us seriously.

644
00:48:11,760 --> 00:48:14,995
是时候坦白了。
Time for the confession.

645
00:48:25,840 --> 00:48:30,110
录制一段视频，读取准确的信息，并将其传播到全世界。
Record a video reading that exact message and stream it to the world.

646
00:48:34,314 --> 00:48:36,917
我想先和我的家人谈谈。
I want to talk to my family first.

647
00:48:36,950 --> 00:48:39,621
-不可能。-你想让我读这个?
- Not a chance. - You want me to read this?

648
00:48:39,654 --> 00:48:41,955
我先和我的家人谈谈。
I talk to my family first.

649
00:48:41,989 --> 00:48:44,793
——或者什么?-不然我不干了。
- Or what? - Or I'm done.

650
00:48:48,362 --> 00:48:51,932
你真是个混蛋，但你确实关心你女儿。
You know, you are a real piece of shit, but you do care about your daughter.

651
00:48:51,965 --> 00:48:53,601
