01:26:23,151 --> 01:26:24,351
好吧?
Okay?

1131
01:26:24,384 --> 01:26:26,554
整个城市都会为你庆祝生日!
The whole city's gonna celebrate your birthday!

1132
01:26:26,587 --> 01:26:27,622
我们走吧。
Let's go.

1133
01:26:56,084 --> 01:26:58,251
更多的间接伤害!
More collateral damage!

1134
01:26:58,285 --> 01:27:01,421
要为你牺牲多少人，奥兰多!
How many gotta die for you, Orlando?!

1135
01:27:03,091 --> 01:27:04,726
哇!
Whoo!

1136
01:27:08,428 --> 01:27:11,431
所以我们终于到达了河的尽头。
So we finally reach the end of the river.

1137
01:27:13,300 --> 01:27:23,376
威拉德千里迢迢带着极端的偏见来消灭库尔茨上校，结果却发现……当他们遇到了……他们是同一个人。
Willard came all this way to eliminate Colonel Kurtz with extreme prejudice, only to find out... when they met... they were the same man.

1138
01:27:25,913 --> 01:27:29,416
来吧，奥兰多!面对你的指挥官!
Come on out, Orlando! Face your commanding officer!

1139
01:27:33,286 --> 01:27:35,590
好吧。好吧。
Okay. Okay.

1140
01:27:36,356 --> 01:27:37,558
我出来。
I'm coming out.

1141
01:27:38,760 --> 01:27:40,695
爸爸来了。
Here comes Daddy.

1142
01:27:50,938 --> 01:27:52,272
停!
Stop!

1143
01:27:55,743 --> 01:27:58,880
奥兰多，请解决这个问题。拜托!
Orlando, please fix this. Please!

1144
01:28:00,280 --> 01:28:02,750
你乱糟糟的。
You fucked up.

1145
01:28:02,784 --> 01:28:06,788
我计划周密，执行周密，士兵。
I had a well-planned, well-executed operation, soldier.

1146
01:28:08,923 --> 01:28:15,096
跟踪，监视，每天听你的嗡嗡声。
Tracking, surveillance, listening to your droning bullshit every fucking day.

1147
01:28:15,129 --> 01:28:16,831
神……他在家也那么无聊吗?
God... is he that boring at home?

1148
01:28:20,101 --> 01:28:21,736
我差一点就成功了。
I was so close.

1149
01:28:22,937 --> 01:28:25,940
你知道我为此付出了多少吗!
Do you have any idea what I put into this?!

1150
01:28:27,275 --> 01:28:30,511
建那个椅架花了多长时间!
How long it took to build that chair rig?!

1151
01:28:30,545 --> 01:28:32,580
是啊，你从哪学的?史泰登岛?
Yeah, where'd you learn that? On Staten Island?

1152
01:28:32,613 --> 01:28:39,854
嗯…当你老爸还在…三角洲的不结盟运动。
Well... you learn a thing or two when your old man was... Delta in 'Nam.

1153
01:28:39,887 --> 01:28:42,023
你的整个人生就是个谎言。
Your whole life is a lie.

1154
01:28:43,591 --> 01:28:45,293
你好的,亲爱的?
You good, honey?

1155
01:28:49,597 --> 01:28:56,938
你也许没朝我爸的脑袋开一枪，但你他妈的让他失去了工作!
You may not have put the bullet in my dad's head, but you fucking took him out of commission!

1156
01:28:59,540 --> 01:29:01,042
他和我妈妈…看着我!
He and my mom... Look at me!

1157
01:29:01,075 --> 01:29:02,375
好吧,好吧。
Okay, okay.

1158
01:29:03,878 --> 01:29:07,014
他们把所有的钱都投给了你那个冒牌公司。
They sunk every penny they had into that sham company of yours.

1159
01:29:07,048 --> 01:29:08,415
你说谎了。
You lied.

1160
01:29:08,448 --> 01:29:11,351
你还不如自己扣动扳机。
You might as well have pulled the trigger yourself.

1161
01:29:11,384 --> 01:29:17,024
奥兰多……我想让你知道…这是你应得的。
Orlando... I need you to know... You deserve this.

1162
01:29:18,425 --> 01:29:20,595
这都是因为你爸爸吗?
So this is all about your dad?

1163
01:29:22,697 --> 01:29:25,365
我的意思是，是也不是。我确实需要你的技能。
I mean, yes and no. I did need your skills.

1164
01:29:26,399 --> 01:29:29,871
杀了你，你知道，那只是…小咖啡馆。
Killing you, you know, that was just a... little perk.

1165
01:29:34,374 --> 01:29:37,044
这是我的罪，不是他们的。
This is my sin, not theirs.

1166
01:29:38,279 --> 01:29:42,717
父亲的罪孽…-放他们走-爸爸，我害怕!
The sins of the father... - Hey, let 'em go. - Dad, I'm scared!

1167
01:29:42,750 --> 01:29:46,087
带我。我可以帮你。我可以帮你消失。
Take me. I can help you. I can help you vanish.

1168
01:29:54,762 --> 01:29:58,966
不，我觉得这变成了自杀任务。
Nah, I think this just became a suicide mission.

1169
01:29:59,000 --> 01:30:01,535
爸爸，我想回家。
Dad, I wanna go home.

1170
01:30:01,569 --> 01:30:04,071
-我们会的，亲爱的-别再骗她了
- We will, honey. - Quit lying to her.

1171
01:30:04,105 --> 01:30:06,974
别再骗你女儿了!这就是你来这里的原因!
Quit lying to your daughter! That's what got you here!

1172
01:30:07,008 --> 01:30:10,745
你的欺骗，你的谎言!你他妈的蛇!
Your deceit, your lies! You fucking snake!

1173
01:30:10,778 --> 01:30:12,079
别撒谎!
Stop lying!

1174
01:30:13,480 --> 01:30:15,016
你知道吗，恩佐?你是对的。
You know what, Enzo? You're right.

1175
01:30:16,483 --> 01:30:17,852
我很喜欢它。
I enjoyed it.

1176
01:30:20,655 --> 01:30:22,556
我很享受这种忙碌。
I enjoyed the rush.

1177
01:30:23,925 --> 01:30:25,660
我很擅长这个。
I was good at it.

1178
01:30:26,527 --> 01:30:28,562
我很擅长。
I am good at it.

1179
01:30:28,596 --> 01:30:30,264
我还会这么做。
And I would do it again.

1180
01:30:30,298 --> 01:30:32,499
尤其是对你老爸这样的笨蛋。
Especially to a sucker like your old man.

1181
01:30:32,533 --> 01:30:34,902
你他妈闭嘴!
Shut the fuck up!

1182
01:30:45,112 --> 01:30:46,180
亲爱的,你明白吗?
Honey, you okay?

1183
01:30:46,213 --> 01:30:47,615
你对吧?
You all right?

1184
01:30:47,648 --> 01:30:49,884
好吧,好吧。好了，我们把这东西拿下来。
Okay, okay. Okay, let's get this thing off of you.

1185
01:30:49,917 --> 01:30:51,352
——好吧?-奥兰多，把它弄下来。
- All right? - Orlando, get it off.

1186
01:31:00,661 --> 01:31:03,864
爸爸……等一下,放松。
Dad... Hang on, relax.

1187
01:31:03,898 --> 01:31:06,567
-倒计时了。-哦,不。
- It's counting down. - Oh, no.

1188
01:31:09,070 --> 01:31:11,739
救命!
Help! Help!

1189
01:31:14,342 --> 01:31:15,843
你打算怎么办?
What are you gonna do?

1190
01:31:15,876 --> 01:31:19,213
你打算怎么办，奥兰多?
What are you gonna do, Orlando?

1191
01:31:20,414 --> 01:31:22,650
再责怪自己吗?
Blame yourself again?

1192
01:31:26,454 --> 01:31:27,855
跑
Run.

1193
01:31:27,888 --> 01:31:31,926
我哪也不去。我呆在这里。去,金。走吧!
I'm not going anywhere. I'm staying here. Go, Kim. Go!

1194
01:31:31,959 --> 01:31:32,693
——不。——走!
- No. - Go!

1195
01:31:32,727 --> 01:31:34,762
——不。-跑…
- No. - Run...

1196
01:31:46,240 --> 01:31:47,475
将军。
Checkmate.

1197
01:31:47,508 --> 01:31:49,677
谢谢你！
Thank you!

1198
01:31:49,710 --> 01:31:51,946
谢谢，谢谢，谢谢。
Thank you, thank you, thank you.

1199
01:32:03,524 --> 01:32:05,826
是的，我在路上了。医院见
Yeah, I'm on my way. See you at the hospital.

1200
01:32:05,860 --> 01:32:09,230
是啊，度假听起来不错。
Yeah, a vacation sounds nice.

1201
01:32:09,263 --> 01:32:11,298
退休听起来更好。
Retirement sounds better.

1202
01:32:16,037 --> 01:32:17,071
是的。
Yep.

1203
01:32:17,104 --> 01:32:19,874
谢谢你的帮忙。
Thanks for helping out.

1204
01:32:19,907 --> 01:32:22,977
是啊，我只是个想修复家庭的人。
Yeah, I'm just a guy trying to fix his family.

1205
01:32:23,010 --> 01:32:26,647
那边那个人，他是英雄。
That guy over there, he's the hero.

1206
01:32:28,549 --> 01:32:30,584
他拯救了我们所有人。
He saved us all.

1207
01:32:30,618 --> 01:32:32,053
把这话告诉报纸，好吗?
Tell that to the papers, okay?

1208
01:32:32,086 --> 01:32:34,889
我们需要你去局里问话。
We're gonna need you downtown for questioning.

1209
01:32:36,390 --> 01:32:38,292
我能和家人单独待一会儿吗?
Can I just have a minute with my family?

1210
01:32:38,325 --> 01:32:39,927
是的。
Yeah.

1211
01:32:45,966 --> 01:32:48,903
你们还在为我错过派对而生气吗?
You guys still mad at me for missing the party?

1212
01:32:51,405 --> 01:32:53,340
我是来补偿你的，好吗?
I'm here to make it up to you, okay?


